Atlanta’s Most Trusted Dog Walking Company
Alfie LLC is bonded, insured, and potty trained. Better than a belly rub – guaranteed.



 
Cutting-Edge Technology
With GPS tracking, real-time notifications, online scheduling and billing, and so much more, Alfie uses the most advanced dog walking and pet sitting software in the world.



 
A Team You Can Rely On
All of our walkers are experienced and proven pet pros, so you can be confident that your pup and your home are in good paws with Alfie.



 
There When You Need Us
Whether it’s everyday or just when you’re stuck at the office, you can count on Alfie when your precious pooch needs us most.

















