Let's Walk!









Meet Our Prefurred Clients
			Many of your friends and neighbors already use Alfie for their dog walking and pet sitting needs! Based in Midtown, our world-class Atlanta dog walkers cover a lot of ground in many areas. From Buckhead to Brookhaven, Morningside to Virginia-Highland, Inman Park to Old Fourth Ward and almost everywhere in between, our dog walking team services nearly all of Atlanta's in-town neighborhoods! Wondering if we service your area? Odds are we do, but simply give us a call or send us an email to find out!		







 



 



 



 



 



 



 



 



 



 

























